Interface LanguageImplementation

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    LanguagePackImplementation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GenericLanguageImplementation, TalismaneEnglish, TalismaneFrench

    public interface LanguageImplementation
    An implementation of Talismane for a specific language.
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
